Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下该到极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村里的守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:45.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来需要增援了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了 上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是送给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是托尼卡村的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看呀 守卫的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 虽然被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像身负重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了些小事故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很便宜哦 新鲜出炉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错吧 大丰收哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏我的技术高超呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑选鱼饵的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没换鱼饵之前一无所获吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太喜欢吃鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法兹 别太挑剔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃起来很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼腥味也大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈在的话 就能做别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在教室里也哼过这首曲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:03:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的幸存者是希塞露的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和我是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩提时曾一起生活过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直管他叫哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经好久没见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到胖成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一点都没变 我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保护了五个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才就开始了 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得肚子里汹涌澎湃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个忍者护额的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是袭击村子人的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是什么可疑的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险 年久失修 请勿过桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧 不行 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是只能逃跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜 走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.59,0:09:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时性急弄错了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们也差点因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露应该认识的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾在村里担任孩子们的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很有勇气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰德和法兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是小空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是雷欧的妹妹米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件背心不嫌大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这原本是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她非常喜欢 不肯脱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜为何想得到那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无头绪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那里到底有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经是名学者 研究过考古学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别对巨坑进行过相当缜密的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是关于巨坑的古文书的研究成果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据考证 这里面记录了某个历史事件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上古之神创造的天之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被污秽之人夺去了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因污秽之人憎恨一切事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,企图利用那份力量毁灭世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股足以颠覆世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要将世界毁于一旦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个亡灵偶然捡到了力量的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化身为身覆赤炎者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向污秽之人复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过七度炼狱的激战之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身覆赤炎者最终获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤炎者为防其他污秽之人玷污力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其分为七个音符并封印在这段音律里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是简要的概括
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音律…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是兜偷的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果确实存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天之矛到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那是超越人类智慧的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实能感觉到那个巨坑中藏有什么重大的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且不说盗取秘宝的恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连无辜的村民都赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事绝不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会让兜偿还所有的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家准备一起去泡露天温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小樱混浴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是传说中的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们进行修炼后 或许也能做到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人在这种乡下地方也是名人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为是个相当强势可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到既年轻又随和 让人大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体里蕴藏着相当了不起的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你一般大时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能救起一个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这道伤疤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前从悬崖下摔了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概有50米高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好挂在树上得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥反复叮嘱我小心些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他立刻抓住了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概有一小时左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直抓着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不爱运动 缺乏腕力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很丢脸 很后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果希塞露死了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是哥哥的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌如此懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦成为了一名守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此付出了努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不太适合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就各奔东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔去看他 总觉得有些尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉就疏远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违的重聚 虽然很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有更强大的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更强…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥肯定很懊恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能救更多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了那么多重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥 告诉我们诀窍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在我打算睡觉时发觉了村子的异常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间 村子便成了火海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被忍者袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我以为自己死定了的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进攻突然停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同断线的木偶一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秽土转生这种忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以活人充当祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将死者的灵魂束缚其中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并强制将其唤醒的禁术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原以为只有第二代火影和大蛇丸会使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙还不能百分之百成功地控制晓的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来忍术不够成熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克先生知道音律吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古文书提到的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来兜的目标是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有关音律 您知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者有供参考的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上这个快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你把它扔在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但绝不可泄露此事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天起 我们将和镇里的警卫队合作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜寻那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然有守卫被抓的先例
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会在您身边安排护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那些得救的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇上的福利院愿意接收他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 这些孩子笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天夜里以来 第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你设计的术式真够乱来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不用赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很有意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你这么觉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸肯定会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用自己的查克拉改良了术式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定能成功控制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该试试拥有意识和记忆的状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.31,0:20:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许被谁拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要让我去找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初不是这么决定的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很会使唤人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉越来越有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孤单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:22:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量 第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.70,0:23:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去 出去 出去 出去 出去…